pd_brief:
On Friday, October 6th the daily rituals began with suprabatham seva followed by abhishekam to Sri Nithyanandeshwara Paramashiva Linga and Sri Kalabhairava on the auspicious occasion of Ashtami. Following alankar, laghu puja was offered to Moolavar, Sri Kalabhairava, Sri Ardhanareeshwara and Shabhda Veda grantha. The morning rituals concluded with the morning naivedyam offering to Moolavar.
Temples rituals started again with pada puja to Swamiji which was followed by evening naivedyam offering to Sri Nithyanandeshwara Paramashiva Linga, Nithyanandeshwara Sandhya aarti to the main sannidhi and finally palliarai seva.
